<p>本周降水过程较多</p>
<p>但整体较弱</p>
<p><img src="//p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201208/61a77017dc0f4bd888a16060db2abda1.jpeg" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
