<p>Mahuangliang loess Geopark in Yulin City, Shaanxi Province (UAV photo) was taken on December 3 after the snow.</p>
<p>On that day, Mahuangliang loess Geopark in Yulin City, Shaanxi Province, located on the Loess Plateau, was beautiful after the snow. Mahuangliang loess Geopark covers a total area of 37 square kilometers. The thick loess layer has been washed by wind and rain for thousands of years, forming a unique geomorphic landscape, which is breathtaking. It has become a good place for people to travel and photograph.</p>
