➜Roundtable: Forging a New Social Contract and Implementing a Global New Deal
http://www.sohu.com/a/437007043_162758	28825
<p>At a roundtable conference on promoting global economic recovery initiated by the United Nations Secretary-General Guterres, he called for the creation of a new social contract and a new global deal, so that the global economy will rejuvenate and bring sustainable development to all.</p>
<p>Guterres delivered a speech at this roundtable on promoting global economic recovery attended by many famous economists. He pointed out that the new crown pandemic has caused more than 1 million deaths and more than 100 million people are being pushed into extreme poverty and hunger. The situation is multiplying, famine is approaching, and inequality is increasing. At the same time, the interruption of education is creating a "lost generation." What is concerning is that the gender equality gap is also widening.</p>
